>很大利益。<span class="_ _8"></span>对此大家可以慢慢体会，<span class="_ _8"></span>若修持利他心，<span class="_ _8"></span>一定会</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y14a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">对自己有极大的帮助。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c h4 y1ee ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我看过一本书叫<span class="_ _a"></span>《致命的情绪》<span class="_ _c"></span>，<span class="_ _a"></span>是一位美国学者写的。</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y1ef ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">其中讲到，<span class="_ _8"></span>一个人如果发脾气，<span class="_ _8"></span>血液就会产生毒素，<span class="_ _8"></span>注射到</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y14d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">动物身上会使其死亡。<span class="_ _8"></span>所以，<span class="_ _8"></span>我们要存一颗善心，<span class="_ _8"></span>这不仅是</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y14e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">佛教提倡的，科学也是这么认为的。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
